3. As per the provisions of Section 4 (4) and Section 4 (5) of the Maharashtra Prevention of Delay in discharge of Government Duties and Regulation of Transfer of Government Employees Act, 2005, the following officers of the cadre of Additional Collector / Additional Collector (Selection) are listed in front of their names in column No. The post indicated in section 4 is being posted with the approval of the competent authority in the interest of public service and administrative convenience.

4. The aforesaid officer is being unilaterally relieved from his present office with effect from the date 11.10.2024 (M.No) for immediate effect at the place of posting. The concerned officer should immediately inform the Government by e-mail / post at e.revenue@maharashtra.gov.in 1 as to the date on which he / she appeared at the place of new appointment.
